  "excerpt": "<p>Katie and I each shared our picks for Valentine’s Day last year and it was an absolute blast seeing what we each picked. See my gifts for him post and Katie’s gifts for her post to check them out. We had so much fun perusing through Etsy that we decided to do it all over again for 2016! I really love seeing how our tastes change over the course of a year.</p>\n",
  "content": "<p>Katie and I each shared our picks for Valentine’s Day last year and it was an absolute blast seeing what we each picked. See my <strong><a href=\"/husbands-etsy-picks-valentines-day-gifts-for-him/\">gifts for him</a></strong> post and Katie’s <strong><a href=\"/my-etsy-picks-valentines-day-gifts-for-her/\">gifts for her</a></strong> post to check them out. We had so much fun perusing through Etsy that we decided to do it all over again for 2016! I really love seeing how our tastes change over the course of a year.</p>\n<p>That said, it seems like my tastes haven’t changed very much after all 🙂 – I still love all things wood, I still want cookies or honey (or anything edible, really) and I absolutely adore any and all blacksmithing things. <strong><em><a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/treasury/MTkxNTU5NTB8MjcyODIxODI1Ng/valentines-day-gifts-for-him-2016\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">If you’d like to shop the original treasury, you can find it right here.</a></em></strong> Otherwise, click each shop below to take you to the item I chose! Enjoy!</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Homestead1227 - Custom State Sign, 1 - Custom Home State Sign - Wooden State Sign - Wood State Sign - Wood Wall Art - Housewarming Gift - Wedding Gift Idea\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/248195780/custom-state-sign-1-custom-home-state?ref=tre-2728218256-1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Homestead1227</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"SweetRoseBakery - Salted Chocolate Chunk Cookies, chocolate chip cookies, homemade baked goods\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/112773145/salted-chocolate-chunk-cookies-chocolate?ref=tre-2728218256-2\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SweetRoseBakery</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"BrandIron - CAMP - nature inspired candle with leather\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/245888543/camp-nature-inspired-candle-with-leather?ref=tre-2728218256-3\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BrandIron</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"TomFellBlacksmith - Leaf Keyring or Keychain, handmade ironwork by Tom Fell - Blacksmith\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/243958234/leaf-keyring-or-keychain-handmade?ref=tre-2728218256-4\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TomFellBlacksmith</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"StonebrookJewelry - Damascus Steel Ring Acid Finish Genuine Craftsmanship Band\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/50973352/damascus-steel-ring-acid-finish-genuine?ref=tre-2728218256-5\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">StonebrookJewelry</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"JooJoobs - iPhone 6 Case, iPhone 6S Leather Case Wallet, iPhone 6 Leather Case Wallet, iPhone 6 PLUS Wallet, iPhone 6S Plus Wallet - [Listing #055]\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/157843227/iphone-6-case-iphone-6s-leather-case?ref=tre-2728218256-6\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JooJoobs</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"RongDesigns - Wood coasters, rustic wood coasters, live edge coasters, round coasters, coasters, valentines, christmas, wedding favours, housewarming gift\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/129361813/wood-coasters-rustic-wood-coasters-live?ref=tre-2728218256-7\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">RongDesigns</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"ToothandSteel - Railroad Spike Knife\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/224914887/railroad-spike-knife?ref=tre-2728218256-8\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ToothandSteel</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"ClickandBlossom - Hubby Ceramic Mug\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/221737501/hubby-ceramic-mug?ref=tre-2728218256-9\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ClickandBlossom</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"BallardForge - Forged Bottle Openers\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/88625157/forged-bottle-openers?ref=tre-2728218256-10\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">BallardForge</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"ElleBellCafe - Cafe Passion, Organic Cameroon Peaberry Coffee, French Roast Coffee Lovers Gift, 1/2 lb Bag, Roasted Coffee Beans, Gourmet Coffee Lover\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/230182857/cafe-passion-organic-cameroon-peaberry?ref=tre-2728218256-11\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ElleBellCafe</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"TimberArtSigns - Kitchen Art Fork Spoon Knife Wooden Wall Plaques Modern Home Decor\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/154804598/kitchen-art-fork-spoon-knife-wooden-wall?ref=tre-2728218256-12\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">TimberArtSigns</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Starknakedsoap - Blue moon Beer Soap, Soap on a Rope, Hemp Rope, fragrance free, Soap for men, Cold Processed, Natural Soap, Vegan Organic, Soap for Men\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/259858242/blue-moon-beer-soap-soap-on-a-rope-hemp?ref=tre-2728218256-13\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Starknakedsoap</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Necklush - Jewelry, Bracelets, For Men, For Boyfriend, For Guys, Boyfriend Birthday, Gift For Brother, Gift Ideas for Him, For Him Birthday, For Dad\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/245072171/jewelry-bracelets-for-men-for-boyfriend?ref=tre-2728218256-14\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Necklush</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"SeedGeeks - Artisan Raw Honey - 16oz (1lb) - All natural, treatment free honey\" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/209226902/artisan-raw-honey-16oz-1lb-all-natural?ref=tre-2728218256-15\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">SeedGeeks</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"CustomNatureLLC - Bob Ross Style Original Landscape Oil Painting - \" href=\"https://www.etsy.com/listing/261783788/bob-ross-style-original-landscape-oil?ref=tre-2728218256-16\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">CustomNatureLLC</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>Which Valentine’s pick do you think the guy in your life will like the most?</p>\n",
